agents.title: Self-Modifying AI Agent System
agents.description: Build a self-modifying AI agent system that creates specialized sub-agents on demand
agents.prompt: Create an AI agent orchestrator that can dynamically spawn custom agents based on runtime needs, with each agent having specific capabilities and tools

agents.title: Real-Time Code Execution Visualizer
agents.description: Create a real-time code visualizer that turns any Python script into an animated execution flow diagram
agents.prompt: Build a tool that visualizes Python code execution in real-time, showing function calls, data flow, and variable states as an animated diagram

agents.title: GitHub Repository Architecture Analyzer
agents.description: Build a GitHub repo analyzer that generates complete architectural documentation and dependency graphs
agents.prompt: Create a tool that analyzes any GitHub repository and automatically generates comprehensive technical documentation with visual dependency maps and architecture diagrams

agents.title: Voice-Controlled Coding Assistant
agents.description: Create a voice-controlled coding assistant that executes natural language commands as code
agents.prompt: Build a system that listens to voice commands like 'refactor this function to use async/await' and automatically modifies code accordingly

agents.title: AI-Powered Framework Migration Tool
agents.description: Build an AI-powered code migration tool that converts entire projects between frameworks
agents.prompt: Create a tool that can automatically migrate entire codebases between frameworks (React to Vue, Express to FastAPI, etc.) while preserving functionality

agents.title: ML-Based Bug Prediction System
agents.description: Create a bug prediction system that analyzes commit history to identify future failure points
agents.prompt: Build a machine learning system that analyzes git commit history and code patterns to predict where bugs are likely to appear before they happen

agents.title: Collaborative AI Coding Competition
agents.description: Build a collaborative coding game where multiple AI agents compete to optimize the same codebase
agents.prompt: Create a system where multiple AI agents with different optimization strategies compete in real-time to improve the same codebase

agents.title: 3D Code Architecture Visualizer
agents.description: Create a code-to-diagram generator that turns any codebase into interactive 3D architecture visualizations
agents.prompt: Build a tool that generates interactive 3D visualizations of code architecture, allowing developers to navigate their code like a video game

agents.title: Automated API Reverse Engineering Tool
agents.description: Build an automated API reverse-engineering tool that generates SDKs from network traffic
agents.prompt: Create a tool that captures API calls and automatically generates fully-typed client libraries in multiple languages with complete documentation

agents.title: Time-Travel Debugging System
agents.description: Create a 'time-travel debugger' that records entire program execution for replay and modification
agents.prompt: Build a debugging system that records complete program execution and allows developers to replay, rewind, and modify any point in the execution history
